## Pandoc-style Markdown links as wiki links

Because WikiMark treats relative-target `[text](page)` links as wiki
pages, these are all wiki links too:
[the home page](Main Page), [help](Help:Editing),
[tutorial](Getting Started),
[introduction](Introduction to WikiMark),
[glossary](Glossary), [FAQ](Frequently Asked Questions),
[changelog](Changelog), [roadmap](Roadmap).

## Sections with references mixed in

The [[Planet]] Earth is the third planet from [[Sun|Sol]]. It has one
natural satellite, the [[Moon]], and two quasi-satellites. Its surface
is approximately 71% water, with the remaining land divided into
continents named [[Africa]], [[Antarctica]], [[Asia]], [[Australia]],
[[Europe]], [[North America]], and [[South America]].

